name: colonial-2-level-4-bed
description: A 15 x 15 meter colonial-style two-level home designed with timeless elegance and balanced proportions, offering 4 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms within a refined and functional layout. The exterior showcases classic symmetry and two welcoming front porches that enhance curb appeal, while a rear porch extends the living space outdoors. Inside, the main level includes a formal living room with a fireplace, a well-appointed kitchen, a dedicated dining room, and a convenient butler pantry that connects seamlessly for entertaining and storage. A walk-in pantry and separate laundry room add everyday practicality. A second fireplace enhances warmth and character within the living areas. Interior stairs provide smooth circulation between floors, leading to private bedroom spaces thoughtfully arranged for comfort and privacy, making this home ideal for both family living and formal gatherings.
